  "texts": [
    "Thus, we did not expect optimal outcomes with this approach and acknowledge that professionals with high skill levels in prompt engineering may generate much better results.",
    "This type of approach was used for all follow-up prompts during the dialogue as well.",
    "The first prompt (no.",
    "1) was followed by a dialogue based on \"follow-up prompts\" (no.",
    "1.1-1.5) since the proposals were either very general (e.g., along the scientific research process) or included a wide variety of procedures until finally two procedures could be narrowed down (see Figure 3, as well as the example for prompt 1.5: \"I meant: would they do PCA or MDS to visualize the objects in a two dimensional space like the theoretical model\")."
